{"tid":1895221,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打同我一樣寧願單身一世都唔會要個非處女朋友？","createTime":"2020-02-24T11:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T23:54:35.000Z","uid":150100,"like":11,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c705a29fe5f48be1b1219a2d3ac96ddc1278e2","tid":1895221,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"花開，然後花謝；星星閃爍，也總有消失之日。這個地球、太陽、銀河系，甚至整個宇宙，都會有死亡的那一天。與這些相比，人類的一生，就好像一眨眼這麼短暫。可就在這段在的一瞬間內，人誕生，歡笑，哭泣，戰鬥，受傷，歡喜，悲傷，憎恨誰，愛上誰&middot;&middot;&middot;所有的一切都是剎那間的邂逅。然後，任何人都會進入名為&ldquo;死亡&rdquo;的永眠中。<br />\n所以，就算一世冇拖拍都冇所謂，一切只是剎那間的邂逅，但係至少畢生都帶住尊嚴而活。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一枝枯萎的鮮花，不會再盛開。人、鳥、蟲&hellip;&hellip;光輝的星星都只有一次生命&hellip;&hellip;，女人嘅處都係。"},{"pid":"dd290d6398036b68e5e5bebb9d1664c0dc21bf9a","tid":1895221,"uid":204943,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"Noted with thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256ae8f6ed6ff1ffcb1d0aa3158e9e1d422d5df3","tid":1895221,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd290d6398036b68e5e5bebb9d1664c0dc21bf9a","tid":1895221,"uid":204943,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"Noted with thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"你拋棄了友誼和眼淚，就毫無勝利的希望了！"},{"pid":"370ccdd191e2b3feabd6dc559342895350d383ce","tid":1895221,"uid":150100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"處是只有一次的。也正因此，它才會發放出無比寶貴的光芒。"},{"pid":"5a90377ad8c49daf1b32013628a5324c4b92b24b","tid":1895221,"uid":150100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"為了處，男人能夠非常溫柔，也能非常堅強！"},{"pid":"cf2059c3a9707a81a86b6edaafdedd60b3d3c883","tid":1895221,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smi